<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #004085;
        }

        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Personal un-assignment</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear [Tutor Name],</p>
            <p>The following tutee. has been un-assigned from your care: <strong>[Student Name]</strong></p>
            <p>You can no longer use the following part of the eTutor system to interact with them:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Message your tutees</li>
                <li>Arrange and record meetings (both real and virtual)</li>
                <li>Upload documents and comment on them</li>
                <li>Access your personal dashboard</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If this un-assignment is incorrect please contact staff within 24 hours to undo this action.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact the support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>